Ing '''Apayao''' metung yang gabun a makakandadung [[Ding Lalawigan ning Filipinas|lalawigan]] ning  [[Filipinas]] king [[Labuad Cordillera]] king [[Luzon]]. Ing kayang balen tungku ya pin ing [[Kabugao, Apayao|Kabugao]] at ing sepu na king pangulu at aslagan king [[Cagayan]], at king albugan ding [[Abra|Abra]] at [[Ilocos Norte]], at king mauli king [[Kalinga]]. Bayu [[1995]], Kalinga at Apayao dati lang metung a lalalwigan at mayayaus lang ''[[Kalinga-Apayao]]'', anggang mikawani lang adua para ayasikasu da ing pamangailangan da ring balang metung a katutubu king karelang lalawigan. Agpang keng {{wikidata|qualifier|single|P1082|P585}} ning sensus, atin yang populasyun a {{PH wikidata|population_total}} a katau kareng {{PH wikidata|household}} a pamimalemale.

